OL,3,CHalf of Britons turned to neighbours
OL,4,Cfor help in past year ` survey
OL,6,FHalf of Britons (50%) have turned to
OL,7,Ftheir neighbours for help over the
OL,8,Fpast 12 months, a survey suggests.
OL,10,FThose in their 20s drove the surge in
OL,11,Fpeople asking neighbours for help,
OL,12,Fwith requests increasing by 35%,
OL,13,Ffollowed by those in their 30s, up
OL,14,F32%, the poll for neighbourhood
OL,15,Fnetwork Nextdoor found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
