OL,3,CHalf of Britons turned to neighbours
OL,4,Cfor help in past year ` survey
OL,6,FOverall, support among neighbours is
OL,7,Fup 19% year on year as people
OL,8,Fincreasingly turn to those living
OL,9,Fclosest to them for practical everyday
OL,10,Fhelp including childcare and household
OL,11,Ffixes.
OL,13,FOne in four people in their 30s (25%)
OL,14,Fasked a neighbour for help and advice,
OL,15,Fwhile 21% in their 20s reported
OL,16,Fneeding support with emergency repairs
OL,17,Fand fixes over the past 12 months.
OL,19,FAlmost one in 10 Britons (9%) have
OL,20,Fturned to neighbours for childcare and
OL,21,Fschool runs in the past year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
