OL,3,CHalf of Britons turned to neighbours
OL,4,Cfor help in past year ` survey
OL,6,FAcross British communities, asking
OL,7,Fneighbours to check on homes was the
OL,8,Fmost popular form of help required
OL,9,F(36%), followed by help moving heavy
OL,10,Fitems and furniture (24%).
OL,12,FMeanwhile, 19% of those who have not
OL,13,Fasked for help said it was because
OL,14,Fthey did not know their neighbours
OL,15,Fwell enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
