OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774832614
OL,3,CHalf of Britons turned to neighbours
OL,4,Cfor help in past year ` survey
OL,6,FAlice Skeats, from Nextdoor, said:
OL,7,F"Our research shows that the appetite
OL,8,Ffor neighbourly connection is there
OL,9,Fbut people just need a way in.
OL,11,F"But too many people are still holding
OL,12,Fback simply because they don't know
OL,13,Fwho is around them.
OL,15,F"When that changes, communities
OL,16,Ffunction differently as they are able
OL,17,Fto respond faster, support one
OL,18,Fanother, and feel more confident
OL,19,Fasking for help."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@QO]
